metadata.name: COLLECTING 1
metadata.description:
this collage is about collecting. 

i'm super grateful for the web3 community and the opportunity to collect art from incredible artists. 

this collage attempts to summarize my experience so far and represents my appreciation for everyone I've met along the way. at the end of the day, it is a giant thank you.

collecting is best learned by doing - everyones experience is different. i have really enjoyed finding communities through artist, companies and dads. it stands true that good people know good people - even on the internet.

a special thanks to collector friends for the community and support, to artist friends for the conversation, learnings and inspiration, and to the builders/dao-ers who make this world possible.

we're only getting started ... and the best is yet to come <3

ps. the book excerpt is Techno Rebels (Dan Sicko), which I happened to read before getting introduced to web3 - the parallels are what initially got me excited + helped me make sense of things.
